ygData.subject: Re: ppl at Runnyeye
ygData.msgSnippet: Runnyeye is one of the most deserted zones in the game. Not much loot there, only blacked stuff. You high level guys can hunt the goblin king and his side
ygData.messageBody:
Runnyeye is one of the most deserted zones in the game. Not much loot there,
only blacked stuff. You high level guys can hunt the goblin king and his side
